      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Determinazione hash md5 della password                    *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       det-md5-pwd-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione valore di uscita                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-det-md5-pwd-md5      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Salvataggio immagine video                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "SV"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Richiesta alla segreteria di un pathname unico  *
      *              * per file temporaneo, e sua memorizzazione       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "UP"                 to   s-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/msegrt"
                                         using s                      .
           move      s-pat                to   w-det-md5-pwd-tpt      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Per convenzione la presenza eventuale di '&'    *
      *              * viene tradotta in '@' per evitare errori di     *
      *              * esecuzione in quanto '&' e' un parametro di     *
      *              * bash                                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           inspect   w-ute-pwd-ute   replacing all "&" by "@"         .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Comando di determinazione                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      80                   to   w-all-str-lun          .
           move      04                   to   w-all-str-num          .
           move      "/abd/etc/t_md5_pwd" to   w-all-str-cat (1)      .
           move      w-ute-pwd-ute        to   w-all-str-cat (2)      .
           move      "| cat >"            to   w-all-str-cat (3)      .
           move      w-det-md5-pwd-tpt    to   w-all-str-cat (4)      .
           perform   all-str-csb-000      thru all-str-csb-999        .
           move      w-all-str-alf        to   o-shs                  .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Richiamo del modulo 'mopsys'                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "SH"                 to   o-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mopsys"
                                         using o                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Erase video                                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "ER"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Ripristino immagine video                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "RS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       det-md5-pwd-300.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Apertura del file temporaneo                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "OI"                 to   g-ope                  .
           move      "siz "               to   g-nam                  .
           move      w-det-md5-pwd-tpt    to   g-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mcvinp"
                                         using g                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se errore : uscita con flag di errore           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        g-sts                =    e-not-err
                     go to det-md5-pwd-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Chiusura del file in input                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "CL"                 to   g-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mcvinp"
                                         using g                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Cancellazione modulo utilizzato                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           cancel    "swd/mod/prg/obj/mcvinp"                         .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Flag di uscita                                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "N"                  to   w-det-md5-pwd-md5      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Ad uscita                                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     det-md5-pwd-900.
       det-md5-pwd-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Read file sequenziale - riga 1                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "GN"                 to   g-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mcvinp"
                                         using g                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se fine file : uscita con flag                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        g-sts                not  = e-not-err
                     go to det-md5-pwd-800.
       det-md5-pwd-500.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Comodo per lettura file                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * In campo di comodo                          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      g-rec                to   w-det-md5-pwd-md5      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * A close                                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     det-md5-pwd-800.
       det-md5-pwd-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Chiusura del file in input                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "CL"                 to   g-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mcvinp"
                                         using g                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Cancellazione modulo utilizzato                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           cancel    "swd/mod/prg/obj/mcvinp"                         .
       det-md5-pwd-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     det-md5-pwd-999.
       det-md5-pwd-999.
           exit.

